			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well a Bard sub at 25, main at 50 would let you have ballad 1, but youre missing so much extra mp it wouldnt be worth the trouble, for 1 at level 50 a BRD or RDM is required in a party, Bard having Ballad and at 55 Ballad 2, and RDM having refresh, this will always be kept on a Summoner so MP regen wont be a big problem, especially with your auto refresh, a WHM sub is much more beneficial to the party so you can continually cure. In a group post 50 a SMN usually replaces the WHM when you have a RDM, so having a SMN with cure is required, a SMN with RDM or BLM sub will have much difficulty finding a party as they can't be as powerful. The SMN job is dependant on having WHM as a sub, which can be unfortunate.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
